# Vercel ignore — prevent these paths from being uploaded to the Vercel build.
#
# `apps/_archive/` is excluded from pnpm workspaces (see pnpm-workspace.yaml)
# but its `package.json` files still poison Vercel's pnpm peer-dep resolver,
# producing `eslint-config-next` variants that aren't in pnpm-lock.yaml. The
# archive is preserved in git per the 90-day retention policy in
# apps/_archive/axiomfolio-vite/README.md; it just must not ride to Vercel.
apps/_archive/
